author: GameSpot
description:
Kurt Indovina and Jean-Luc Seipke discuss their first impressions on the Elder Scolls Olbivion remaster now that we've all had a few days to play. They discuss the leaked screenshots, changes to gameplay, and how the game will fare with fans in the long run.

0:00 - Kurt and Jean-Luc Discuss Elder Scrolls Oblivion Remaster
2:50 - A Humble Apology From Jean-Luc
7:30 - Thoughts On The Combat In Oblivion Remaster
10:44 - Being Able To Sprint
12:34 - This Game Has It's Own Jank?
15:21 - How Do 2 Games Co-Exist That Are The Same?
